ear-and-tear in Windows by installing software into an isolated sandbox.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong><a href=\"Downloads\">Download Sandboxie now<\/a> and give it a try!<\/strong><\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p><strong>Check out the <a href=\"helptopics\">Help Topics<\/a> for sandboxie, or visit the <a href=\"allpages\">Support Page Index<\/a>.<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tired of dealing with rogue software, spyware and malware? Spent too many hours removing unsolicited software? Worried about clicking unfamiliar Web links? Introducing Sandboxie Sandboxie runs your programs in an isolated space which prevents them from making permanent changes to other programs and data in your computer. The red arrows indicate changes flowing from a &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/sandboxie\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Sandboxie<\/span> <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/108"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=108"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/108\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1580,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/108\/revisions\/1580"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=108"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}